OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783835341
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran after another ship is
OL,4,Cattacked in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe United States attacked Iran early
OL,7,Fon Sunday morning over an Iranian
OL,8,Fstrike on a vessel in the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz.
OL,11,FIran apparently responded with attacks
OL,12,Ftargeting Bahrain, Kuwait, Qatar and
OL,13,Fthe United Arab Emirates.
OL,15,FThe US military's Central Command said
OL,16,Fit hit some 140 targets in the
OL,17,Fstrikes, far more than the last two
OL,18,Frounds, and went after missile and
OL,19,Fdrone launch sites, ammunition dumps,
OL,20,Fcommunication equipment and other
OL,21,Fsites.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783835341
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran after another ship is
OL,4,Cattacked in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe attacks "degrade Iran's ability to
OL,7,Fattack civilian mariners and
OL,8,Fcommercial vessels freely transiting
OL,9,Fthe strait," it said.
OL,11,FThe strait has become the key sticking
OL,12,Fpoint in any further negotiations
OL,13,Fbetween Iran and the United States to
OL,14,Ffind a permanent end to the war that
OL,15,Fbegan back at the end of February.
OL,26,@nD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783835341
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran after another ship is
OL,4,Cattacked in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FAbout a fifth of all traded oil and
OL,7,Fnatural gas passed through the strait
OL,8,Fbefore the war began. Iran's grip on
OL,9,Fit during the war led to a global
OL,10,Fenergy crisis, though oil prices have
OL,11,Fsharply dropped since wartime highs of
OL,12,F$120 a barrel.
OL,14,FThe new crossfire in the Persian Gulf
OL,15,Fcomes days after US President Donald
OL,16,FTrump suggested an interim deal in the
OL,17,FIran war was "over."
OL,19,FUS Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth
OL,20,Fwrote online: "Iran made a poor
OL,21,Fchoice. Now they pay."
OL,26,@yD@NOUyD@TO]|D@OOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783835341
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran after another ship is
OL,4,Cattacked in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FMohammad Bagher Qalibaf, the speaker
OL,7,Fof Iran's parliament and a main
OL,8,Fnegotiator, responded.
OL,10,F"The era of one-sided deals is OVER,"
OL,11,Fhe wrote on X. "We told you: keep your
OL,12,Fword or pay the price. Reality is
OL,13,Fknocking."
