PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783835341
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran after another ship is
OL,4,Cattacked in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe United Arab Emirates warned the
OL,7,Fpublic Sunday of an incoming missile
OL,8,Fand drone attack as explosions could
OL,9,Fbe heard in nearby Qatar. A missile
OL,10,Falert sounded in Qatar shortly after
OL,11,Fthe blasts. Qatar's military said in a
OL,12,Fstatement it intercepted the incoming
OL,13,FIranian fire.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, missile alerts sounded in
OL,16,FBahrain, an island kingdom in the
OL,17,FPersian Gulf home to the U.S. Navy's
OL,18,F5th Fleet. Kuwait's military said it
OL,19,Fwas intercepting incoming fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783835341
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran after another ship is
OL,4,Cattacked in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIt wasn't immediately clear what
OL,7,Flocations were under attack in the
OL,8,FUAE, which so far hadn't been targeted
OL,9,Fin the latest round of attacks by
OL,10,FIran. The latest attack on the
OL,11,FEmirates, home to Abu Dhabi and Dubai,
OL,12,Fcame in May when a drone sparked a
OL,13,Ffire on the edge of the country's sole
OL,14,Fnuclear power plant.
OL,16,FIran also made a series of claims
OL,17,Fabout attacks elsewhere that were not
OL,18,Fimmediately confirmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
