PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783835341
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran after another ship is
OL,4,Cattacked in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIn the Strait of Hormuz attack, a
OL,7,FCyprus-flagged container ship was hit
OL,8,Fby Iran and suffered "significant
OL,9,Fengine room damage" and a civilian
OL,10,Fcrew member is missing, US Central
OL,11,FCommand said.
OL,13,FThe United Kingdom Maritime Trade
OL,14,FOperations centre, overseen by the
OL,15,FBritish military, said the ship had
OL,16,Fbeen traveling in a route hugging the
OL,17,Fshoreline of Oman.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@SO]
