CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1783835341
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran after another ship is
OL,4,Cattacked in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThat has been the way ships have
OL,7,Fentered and exited the Persian Gulf
OL,8,Fwhile avoiding Iranian territorial
OL,9,Fwaters. The ship's crew abandoned the
OL,10,Fvessel as it was ablaze, the centre
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
